SUMMARY:Twelfth Night Ensemble
DESCRIPTION:Influenced by the sounds of today\, and with a vision for the future\, the New York–based Twelfth Night Ensemble was formed “with the firm belief that art is best explored as a meeting place of the past\, present\, and future.” Timeless works by Handel\, Vivaldi\, Marais\, J. S. Bach\, and Destouches offer an illuminating vantage point and thoroughly rewarding musical experience in this unique exploration of humanity’s relationship to nature. \n\nEvents are offered for informational\, entertainment\, and educational purposes only. Read Town Hall’s Program Content Policy.
URL:https://townhallseattle.org/event/twelfth-night-ensemble/
